node.text: EMERGEMCY ‼️ Time to wake up!! Men n Women I t’s time to stand for your freedoms. For your kids for your family. If you do one thing for me listen to this podcast ! This is not a pick a side thing. It’s a stand for your freedoms thing. I’m standing for yours and mine! We must stand together and start saying NO! Now do you see why they want us divided ! Police and Military we love you! Please stand for us. Please do not inforce things you know are wrong and Unconstitutional it’s the Oath you took. Your loosing your freedom of choice now. Stand now ! Quit ignoring it will not go away . I already made my living . The place this country is heading that opportunity for you to get ahead will be gone ! Divide and conquer its here. Stand for your kids your family your friends your fellow Americans. The mass majority believe the same thing . Censorship and communism are here. This is the country where you had the right to say NO! Are you worried if you speak up or rep a American flag you will be punished in some way ? That is communism / censorship. This is the best country In the world and it is worth standing for.  I say this with complete compassion for all my fellow citizens.  Please take the time to click the link in my bio and I couldn’t say it any better than @andyfrisella and @granderson33 do. There is some explicit language but I think it is a good thing for everyone to listen to as if you’re worried have you truly paid attention to what our kids are fed on the Internet and in our schools now. Quit complaining how they are taking away things when it is really your job to teach your kids the morals they need such as the Bible and to fly the American flag at your house or business make a stand . This is your country ! Our Country!! Godbless  I pray for your courage . Yes you can make a difference.  #UnitedWeStand #Love #Strength .. podcast on iTunes  Real AF episode 129.  PLEASE SHARE IF ITS ALL U DO ‼️‼️

🦅🦅Bald Eagle 🦅🦅stopped by this morning to eat. Can’t get more bad ass then that ! Had to share this with you.  Pretty Cool. Reminded me that this is such a great country. We must keep it that way. Freedoms don’t come for free you must fight for them daily . 💪🏼 🇺🇸 #Freedom #America

node.text: Well that was a crazy race. Haiden started with a far outside gate pick got going crashed on the first lap. Got back up put on a good charge from behind which was fun to watch got into a little battle with @krystian.janik_27 And after he passed him he missed his shift lost drive tried to get out of the way and guessed wrong on where Janik was going . He thought Janik would stay outside following the outside line he was in as u can see him look left for him. Simple mistake and racing things happen really fast. Janik is a buddy. Purely a racing incident. Must say the announcers got it wrong Way wrong. But that happens. We’re all human.  Main thing is haiden is not seriously Injured . Bumped and and bruised but not giving up ! Thx to everyone who checked on haiden and have our back.💪🏼 #Racing #moto is #gnarly @octaneco
